commit.title: [test-suite] Register `core.eq.type` as it is used by `discriminate`
commit.message:
[test-suite] Register `core.eq.type` as it is used by `discriminate`

It is very surprising that before the error was catched by the tactic,
however it succeeded to prove the inequality:

```coq
Goal O = S O -> Empty.
 discriminate 1.
Qed.
```
